    <title>Python爬取疫情实战</title>
    <url>/2020/10/13/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="项目概述"><a href="#项目概述" class="headerlink" title="项目概述"></a>项目概述</h2><h3 id="项目效果"><a href="#项目效果" class="headerlink" title="项目效果"></a>项目效果</h3><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201013165615673.png" alt="image-20201013165615673" />





<h3 id="项目介绍"><a href="#项目介绍" class="headerlink" title="项目介绍"></a>项目介绍</h3><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV177411j7qJ?p=1">项目学习地址</a></p>
<p>本项目是Python + Flask + Echarts打造的疫情监控系统，涉及的技术有：</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<ul>
<li>Python 网络爬虫</li>
<li>使用 Python与MySQL数据库交互</li>
<li>使用Flask构建Web项目</li>
<li>基于Echarts数据可视化展示</li>
<li>在Linux上部署web项目及爬虫</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="项目架构"><a href="#项目架构" class="headerlink" title="项目架构"></a>项目架构</h3><p>数据获取 –&gt; 数据持久化 –&gt; flask搭建web后台 –&gt; 数据可视化 h5 + echarts</p>
<p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201013171114384.png" alt="image-20201013171114384"></p>
<h3 id="项目环境"><a href="#项目环境" class="headerlink" title="项目环境"></a>项目环境</h3><ul>
<li>Python 3.6</li>
<li>MySQL 5.7</li>
<li>PyCharm（Python IDE）</li>
<li>Jupyter notebook（Python IDE）</li>
<li>HBuild （前端IDE）</li>
<li>Linux主机 （后期项目部署）</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>修改Jupyter工作目录</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>打开cmd输入<code>jupyter notebook --generate-config</code>创建配置文件，可以看到生成在<code>C:\Users\66\.jupyter\jupyter_notebook_config.py</code>目录下</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201013172200612.png" alt="image-20201013172200612"></p>
<ol start="2">
<li><p>打开该文件搜索notebook_dir并取消改行注释，将路径修改为想要存放的工作路径，并且添加r让\不被转义</p>
<p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201013172912102.png" alt="image-20201013172912102"></p>
</li>
<li><p>工作路径下新建记事本并修改成<code>start.cmd</code>，在该记事本中写入<code>jupyter notebook</code>，以后双击该文件变自动打开Jupyter</p>
<p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201013173629714.png" alt="image-20201013173629714"></p>
</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>notebook常用快捷键</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>单元格类型转换：Y、M</li>
<li>插入单元格：A、B</li>
<li>进入命令模式：Esc</li>
<li>运行单元格： ctrl / shift / alt + enter</li>
<li>删除单元格： DD</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="数据获取"><a href="#数据获取" class="headerlink" title="数据获取"></a>数据获取</h2><h3 id="爬虫概述"><a href="#爬虫概述" class="headerlink" title="爬虫概述"></a>爬虫概述</h3><p><strong><font color=red>爬虫就是给网站发起请求，并从响应中提取需要数据的自动化程序</font></strong></p>
<p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201014152738782.png" alt="image-20201014152738782"></p>
<h3 id="urllib发送请求"><a href="#urllib发送请求" class="headerlink" title="urllib发送请求"></a>urllib发送请求</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> urllib <span class="keyword">import</span> request</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;https://www.baidu.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">res = request.urlopen(url)  <span class="comment"># 获取响应</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(res.info())  <span class="comment"># 获取响应头</span></span><br><span class="line">print(res.getcode())  <span class="comment"># 获取状态码</span></span><br><span class="line">print(res.geturl())  <span class="comment"># 获取访问网址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">html = res.read()</span><br><span class="line">html = html.decode(<span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="comment"># 解码</span></span><br><span class="line">print(html)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> urllib <span class="keyword">import</span> request</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;http://www.dianping.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加header信息是最基本的反爬措施</span></span><br><span class="line">header = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/86.0.4240.75 Safari/537.36&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">req = request.Request(url,headers=header)</span><br><span class="line">res = request.urlopen(req)  <span class="comment"># 获取响应</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(res.info())</span><br><span class="line">print(res.getcode())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201027163120933.png" alt="image-20201027163120933"></p>
<h3 id="requests发送请求"><a href="#requests发送请求" class="headerlink" title="requests发送请求"></a>requests发送请求</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;https://www.baidu.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">res = requests.get(url)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(res.encoding)</span><br><span class="line">print(res.headers)  <span class="comment"># 里面如果没有&#x27;Content-Type&#x27;，那么encoding=utf-8，否则如果有charset则以设置为准，否则就是ISO-8859-1。</span></span><br><span class="line">print(res.url)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">res.encoding = <span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">print(res.text)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;http://www.dianping.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">header = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/86.0.4240.75 Safari/537.36&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">res = requests.get(url, headers=header)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(res.encoding)</span><br><span class="line">print(res.headers)</span><br><span class="line">print(res.url)</span><br><span class="line">print(res.status_code)</span><br><span class="line">print(res.text)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="使用beautifulsoup4解析内容"><a href="#使用beautifulsoup4解析内容" class="headerlink" title="使用beautifulsoup4解析内容"></a>使用beautifulsoup4解析内容</h3><p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201027165858356.png" alt="image-20201027165858356"></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;http://wsjkw.sc.gov.cn/scwsjkw/gzbd/fyzt.shtml&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">res = requests.get(url)</span><br><span class="line">res.encoding = <span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">html = res.text</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(html)</span><br><span class="line">soup.find(<span class="string">&quot;h2&quot;</span>).text</span><br><span class="line">a = soup.find(<span class="string">&quot;a&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(a)</span><br><span class="line">print(a.attrs)</span><br><span class="line">print(a.attrs[<span class="string">&quot;href&quot;</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url_new = <span class="string">&quot;http://wsjkw.sc.gov.cn&quot;</span> + a.attrs[<span class="string">&quot;href&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">res = requests.get(url_new)</span><br><span class="line">res.encoding = <span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(res.text)</span><br><span class="line">context = soup.find_all(<span class="string">&quot;p&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(context[<span class="number">1</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="使用re解析内容"><a href="#使用re解析内容" class="headerlink" title="使用re解析内容"></a>使用re解析内容</h3><p><img src="/images/Python%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98/image-20201027175326760.png" alt="image-20201027175326760"></p>
<h2 id="Web程序开发"><a href="#Web程序开发" class="headerlink" title="Web程序开发"></a>Web程序开发</h2><h2 id="项目部署"><a href="#项目部署" class="headerlink" title="项目部署"></a>项目部署</h2>]]></content>
