    <title>（三）Siamese Neural Networks for One-shot Image Recognition</title>
    <url>/2020/10/19/%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89Siamese%20Neural%20Networks%20for%20One-shot%20Image%20Recognition/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="论文简介"><a href="#论文简介" class="headerlink" title="论文简介"></a>论文简介</h2><p><strong>Siamese Neural Networks for One-shot Image Recognition</strong></p>
<p>作者单位：Department of Computer Science, University of Toronto. Toronto, Ontario, Canada</p>
<p>作者团队：Gregory Koch  、Richard Zemel、Ruslan Salakhutdinov</p>
<p><a href="https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~rsalakhu/papers/oneshot1.pdf">论文地址</a></p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/kevinzakka/one-shot-siamese">代码地址</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="概要"><a href="#概要" class="headerlink" title="概要"></a>概要</h2><p>通过训练同类物体或者不同类物体的pair，使得同类图片的距离尽可能小，不同类别的距离尽可能大。</p>
<p><img src="/images/%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89Siamese%20Neural%20Networks%20for%20One-shot%20Image%20Recognition/2020080312560847.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<h2 id="网络架构"><a href="#网络架构" class="headerlink" title="网络架构"></a>网络架构</h2><p>网络主要用了卷积、最大池化、ReLU等。</p>
<p><img src="/images/%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89Siamese%20Neural%20Networks%20for%20One-shot%20Image%20Recognition/20200803130808990.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<h4 id="loss-function"><a href="#loss-function" class="headerlink" title="loss function"></a>loss function</h4><p>用的是二分类交叉熵，加了L2正则化项，防止过拟合</p>
<p><img src="/images/%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89Siamese%20Neural%20Networks%20for%20One-shot%20Image%20Recognition/20200803130439341.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<h4 id="optimization"><a href="#optimization" class="headerlink" title="optimization"></a>optimization</h4><p><img src="/images/%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89Siamese%20Neural%20Networks%20for%20One-shot%20Image%20Recognition/20200803130555557.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>回来补上，老师希望我用测量的方式将船舶与AIS融合。</p>
]]></content>
